Description: Join us for Open Source Friday as we chat with Laurent Cozic, creator of Joplin, the open source note-taking app focused on privacy and user control. Laurent will share the story behind Joplin, demo some of its key features, and answer your questions live. Whether you’re curious about open source development, privacy-focused tools, or want to get involved as a contributor, this session is for you!
Author: GitHub
Title: Open Source Friday: Joplin – Open Source Note-taking & Privacy
